Hi, I'm Mo 👋

I build AI systems, data pipelines, and developer tools that turn messy data into useful intelligence.

Most of my work is hands-on engineering — building production-style systems for LLMs, RAG pipelines, data infrastructure, and scalable AI workflows using Python, Docker, and Kubernetes.

I focus on practical implementations that engineers can study, run, and extend.

