ETL systems, data pipelines, feature engineering, analytics workflows

⚙️ Scalable AI Infrastructure
Dockerized microservices, Kubernetes orchestration, autoscaling AI workloads

🔎 Search & Knowledge Systems
Vector search, Pinecone, knowledge retrieval pipelines, document Q&A systems

🧩 Automation & AI Workflows
LangChain pipelines, agent workflows, API integrations, developer tooling

📊 Analytics & Decision Systems
Data analysis, experimentation frameworks, marketing analytics, KPI dashboards

Current Focus

